## Before You Book a Call — Read This First

Most SEO engagements fail because of mismatched expectations, not bad work. You expect specific outcomes by a specific date; the agency delivers activity reports. You expected the senior person; you got an account manager. You expected strategy; you got a keyword spreadsheet.

This page exists to eliminate that gap. By the time you finish reading it, you will know exactly what a monthly SEO retainer with me looks like, what it costs, what you need to bring, and whether it is genuinely the right fit for your business right now.

If it is not the right fit — I will tell you that on the call. I only take on clients I am confident I can help.

