## Retainer Pricing

| Tier | Monthly Investment | Typical Scope |
|---|---|---|
| **Foundation** | £1,500/month | Strategy, monthly session, technical oversight, 2 content briefs, direct access |
| **Growth** | £2,500/month | Everything in Foundation + 4 content briefs, increased technical oversight, competitor monitoring |
| **Accelerated** | £4,000/month | Everything in Growth + 8 content briefs, content review and refresh programme, weekly check-ins |
| **Enterprise** | £5,000+/month | Custom scope for complex sites, multiple keyword clusters, or high-volume content programmes |

Most small to medium businesses working with me are on the Growth tier. Professional services firms and technology companies with mature content programmes typically operate at Accelerated or above.

**Initial project options** — if you are not yet ready for a retainer, a [technical SEO audit](/services/technical-seo-audit) (from £500) or [topical map](/services/topical-maps) (from £800) is the right starting point. These are standalone deliverables with no ongoing commitment required.

All retainers are monthly rolling — no minimum contract. Clients stay because the work compounds, not because they are locked in.

