## Who the Retainer Is Right For

**Professional services firms** — solicitors, accountants, financial advisers, HR consultancies, and management consultancies who need to build topical authority and trust signals in regulated markets. [Full guide to professional services SEO →](/services/professional-services-seo)

**B2B technology and SaaS companies** who need to capture the full research journey — from awareness through to commercial consideration — in competitive software markets. [B2B SEO →](/services/b2b-seo) · [SaaS SEO →](/services/saas-seo)

**E-commerce businesses** competing nationally with complex product catalogues, faceted navigation challenges, and content programmes that need strategic structure. [Ecommerce SEO →](/services/ecommerce-seo-consultant)

**Local service businesses in Reading, Berkshire, and the Thames Valley** who want consistent, senior-level attention rather than an agency account model. [SEO Consultant Reading →](/services/seo-consultant-reading)

**Not the right fit:** businesses with a sub-6-month window, start-ups with fewer than 10 pages of content, or businesses looking for a guaranteed first-page ranking within 60 days.

